@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Inicio — ContactManager Web</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0B0B10;
            --bg-card: rgba(28, 28, 38, 0.5);
            --accent: #6B5BFF;
            --accent-glow: rgba(107, 91, 255, 0.3);
            --text-muted: #8A8A9E;
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; }
        
        body { 
            background-color: var(--bg); 
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, rgba(107, 91, 255, 0.08), transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 90%, rgba(163, 150, 255, 0.05), transparent 40%);
            color: white; 
            height: 100vh; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* --- NAVBAR SIMPLE PARA EL HOME --- */
        .navbar {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            padding: 25px 60px; position: absolute; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 10;
        }

        .brand-name { 
            font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.4rem; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            color: white; text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .brand-name span { color: var(--accent); }

        .team-badge {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* --- CONTENEDOR PRINCIPAL (HERO SECTION) --- */
        .hero-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
            height: 100%;
            gap: 60px;
        }

        /* Lado Izquierdo (Texto y Botones) */
        .hero-text {
            flex: 1;
            animation: slideInLeft 1s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) forwards;
        }

        .pill-badge {
            display: inline-block; background: rgba(107, 91, 255, 0.15); color: #BDB2FF;
            padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(107, 91, 255, 0.3);
            font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 25px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        h1 { 
            font-size: 4.2rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 25px; 
        }
        
        h1 .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #BDB2FF, var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        p { 
            color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 45px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 500px;
        }

        .action-buttons { display: flex; gap: 20px; }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #8375FF); color: white; text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px var(--accent-glow);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); filter: brightness(1.15); box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(107, 91, 255, 0.5); }
        .btn-primary .icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--bg-card); color: white; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; transition: 0.3s; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); transform: translateY(-3px); }

        /* Lado Derecho (Imagen/Ilustración Decorativa) */
        .hero-visual {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeInRight 1.2s ease-out forwards;
        }

        /* Círculos decorativos de fondo */
        .circle-bg {
            position: absolute; width: 450px; height: 450px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(107, 91, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%; z-index: 1;
            animation: pulseBg 4s infinite alternate;
        }

        .glass-panel {
            position: relative; z-index: 2;
            background: rgba(28, 28, 38, 0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 30px; padding: 40px; backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; width: 100%; max-width: 400px;
            transform: rotate(-2deg); transition: 0.5s;
        }
        
        .glass-panel:hover { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.02); }

        /* Mockup de tarjetas de contacto dentro del panel */
        .mockup-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 16px; padding: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .mockup-avatar {
            width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .c1 { background: rgba(107, 91, 255, 0.2); color: #BDB2FF; }
        .c2 { background: rgba(255, 191, 36, 0.2); color: #FBBF24; }
        .c3 { background: rgba(85, 255, 170, 0.2); color: #55FFAA; }

        .mockup-info div:first-child { height: 12px; width: 120px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .mockup-info div:last-child { height: 8px; width: 80px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 4px; }

        /* Animaciones */
        @@keyframes slideInLeft {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50px); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        @@keyframes fadeInRight {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(50px) scale(0.9); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0) scale(1); }
        }

        @@keyframes pulseBg {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* Responsivo */
        @@media (max-width: 900px) {
            .hero-container { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; justify-content: center; gap: 40px; }
            .hero-text { animation: slideUp 1s forwards; }
            .hero-visual { display: none; /* Ocultamos la imagen en celulares para que no estorbe */ }
            h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
            p { margin: 0 auto 30px auto; }
            .action-buttons { justify-content: center; flex-direction: column; }
            .navbar { padding: 20px; justify-content: center; }
            .team-badge { display: none; }
        }

        @@keyframes slideUp {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="#" class="brand-name">
            <span style="font-size:1.6rem;">📒</span> ContactManager<span>.</span>
        </a>
        <div class="team-badge">EQUIPO 8 — 2026</div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-container">
        
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Organiza tu red <br> de contactos con <span class="highlight">inteligencia</span>.</h1>
            <p>Un espacio unificado para gestionar tu agenda, administrar categorías y tener a tu equipo, amigos y clientes a un clic de distancia.</p>
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Contactos")" class="btn-primary">
                    <span class="icon">👥</span> Abrir Agenda
                </a>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Categorias")" class="btn-secondary">
                    <span class="icon">📁</span> Categorías
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual">
            <div class="circle-bg"></div>
            
            <div class="glass-panel">
                <div class="mockup-card">
                    <div class="mockup-avatar c1">L</div>
                    <div class="mockup-info"><div></div><div></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mockup-card">
                    <div class="mockup-avatar c2">J</div>
                    <div class="mockup-info"><div></div><div></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mockup-card">
                    <div class="mockup-avatar c3">D</div>
                    <div class="mockup-info"><div></div><div></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>